{"tid":2005882,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【你識邊個？】盤點淪落拍AV的AKB舊將","createTime":"2020-05-07T11:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T07:30:18.000Z","uid":1426,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9cc9638774c3d096f65e341358e855acc7560f3a","tid":2005882,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T11:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180629/photo/bkn-20180629101513814-0629_00862_001_01p.jpg?20180629163911\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180629101513814-0629_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20180629163911&h=c2ac043b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女星轉咗發展路線，事業真係一定會好咗？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本偶像女團AKB48家族人多勢眾，競爭激烈，在僧多粥少之下，不少成員離隊後另謀出路，轉戰AV界拍攝愛情動作片，反而成功闖出一片天。<br />\n<br />\n中西里菜<br />\n<br />\n中西里菜是AKB的初代主將，離隊後為幫家人還債，改名「山口里子」下海拍AV，之後奉子成婚引退。<br />\n<br />\n橘梨紗<br />\n<br />\n原名高松惠理的橘梨紗是AKB的第九期生，2013年被發現下海拍攝AV，但人氣曇花一現，最後低調引退。<br />\n<br />\n三上悠亞 <br />\n<br />\n原名鬼頭桃菜的三上悠亞，本來是姊妹組合SKE48成員，因流出與尊尼偶像手越祐也的激咀照而離隊。三上轉AV界後大紅，成為新一代亞洲AV小天后。<br />\n<br />\n渡邊茉莉繪<br />\n<br />\nAKB48第1期研究生渡邊茉莉繪，離隊後曾做模特兒一段時間。她上月被網民發現疑拍攝素人AV後，宣布將改名「水嶋那奈」於8月3日推出處女AV。<br />\n<br />\n渡邊麻友<br />\n<br />\n曾於AKB總選舉獲得第一位，離隊後發展一直不如意。2019年12月起一直失蹤後，於2020年5月宣布於SOD拍攝處女AV。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180629/photo/bkn-20180629101513814-0629_00862_001_02b.jpg?20180629163911\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180629101513814-0629_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20180629163911&h=7656f8b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三上悠亞轉戰AV後走紅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180629/photo/bkn-20180629101513814-0629_00862_001_03b.jpg?20180629163911\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180629101513814-0629_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20180629163911&h=f7739d91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中西里菜傳為替父母還債而下海。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180629/photo/bkn-20180629101513814-0629_00862_001_04b.jpg?20180629163911\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180629101513814-0629_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20180629163911&h=c66baae6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中西里菜離開AKB後，改名山口里子拍AV。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180629/photo/bkn-20180629101513814-0629_00862_001_05b.jpg?20180629163911\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180629101513814-0629_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20180629163911&h=474ecfc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n渡邊茉莉繪將於8月在AV界出道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180629/photo/bkn-20180629101513814-0629_00862_001_06b.jpg?20180629163911\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180629101513814-0629_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20180629163911&h=1f5066e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n橘梨紗曾是AKB的第九期生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zQYmdh3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzQYmdh3.jpg&h=b79d5b78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n渡邊麻友曾於AKB總選舉獲得第一位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180629/bkn-20180629101513814-0629_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180629%2Fbkn-20180629101513814-0629_00862_001.html&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdcls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=ec5c1269\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180629/bkn-20180629101513814-0629_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"cb4ae87bcd3643b08aa656f9e609ee5ea114cc21","tid":2005882,"uid":10290,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T11:47:54